OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FMicrosoft co-founder Bill Gates
OL,8,Faddressed his links to convicted
OL,9,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein and
OL,10,Fadmitted to having affairs with two
OL,11,FRussian women in a meeting with staff
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, according to reports.
OL,14,FThe American businessman acknowledged
OL,15,Fthe affairs in a town hall meeting of
OL,16,FGates Foundation employees, according
OL,17,Fto the Wall Street Journal, adding
OL,18,Fthat Epstein had later found out about
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
