OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772118239
OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,F"I did have affairs, one with a
OL,8,FRussian bridge player who met me at
OL,9,Fbridge events, and one with a Russian
OL,10,Fnuclear physicist who I met through
OL,11,Fbusiness activities," Mr Gates
OL,12,Freportedly said.
OL,14,F"I did nothing illicit. I saw nothing
OL,15,Fillicit," he is understood to have
OL,16,Ftold staff.
