OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FMr Gates appears multiple times in the
OL,8,FUS Department of Justice's (DOJ)
OL,9,Frelease of the so-called Epstein files
OL,10,Famid an ongoing investigation into the
OL,11,Flate paedophile financier's
OL,12,Fconnections.
OL,14,FThe documents include email
OL,15,Fcorrespondence between Mr Gates and
OL,16,FEpstein about philanthropic projects,
OL,17,Fcalendar entries documenting dates
OL,18,Fthey got together, and photos of Mr
OL,19,FGates at events the two men attended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
