OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772118239
OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FMr Gates has not been accused of any
OL,8,Fwrongdoing in connection with the
OL,9,Ffiles and denies any knowledge of
OL,10,FEpstein's crimes.
OL,12,FHe has previously said he had met with
OL,13,Fthe disgraced financier to discuss
OL,14,Fphilanthropy, including raising money
OL,15,Ffor global health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
