OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FThe Wall Street Journal reports that
OL,8,FMr Gates told staff he "never spent
OL,9,Fany time with victims" of Epstein and
OL,10,Fapologised for bringing Gates
OL,11,FFoundation executives into meetings
OL,12,Fwith the convicted sex offender.
OL,14,FExplaining to his staff photographs in
OL,15,Fthe Epstein files showing him with
OL,16,Fwomen whose faces are redacted, Mr
OL,17,FGates reportedly told the meeting that
OL,18,Fthe convicted paedophile had asked to
OL,19,Ftake pictures of his assistants with
OL,20,FMr Gates after meetings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
