OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FThe DOJ's release shows the pair had
OL,8,Fscheduled meetings 2014 ` years after
OL,9,FEpstein's 2008 conviction for
OL,10,Fsoliciting a minor.
OL,12,FMr Gates reportedly told staff at
OL,13,FTuesday's meeting that he was aware of
OL,14,Fsome "18-month thing" that had limited
OL,15,FEpstein's travel but that he didn't
OL,16,Fcheck his background properly.
