OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772118239
OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FIn a statement sent to ITV News, a
OL,8,FGates Foundation spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"This was a scheduled townhall with
OL,10,Femployees, which Bill does twice a
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"In the conversation, Bill answered
OL,14,Fquestions submitted by foundation
OL,15,Fstaff on a range of issues, including
OL,16,Fthe release of the Epstein files, the
OL,17,Ffoundation's work in AI, and the
OL,18,Ffuture of global health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
