OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,F"In the town hall, Bill spoke
OL,8,Fcandidly, addressing several questions
OL,9,Fin detail, and took responsibility for
OL,10,Fhis actions."
OL,12,FIn an interview with Australia's
OL,13,FWHAS11 news earlier this month, Mr
OL,14,FGates said: "Every minute I spent with
OL,15,Fhim I regret and I apologise that I
OL,16,Fdid that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
