OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,F"I never went to (Epstein's) island. I
OL,8,Fnever met any women, and so the more
OL,9,Fthat comes out the more clear it'll be
OL,10,Fthat although the time was a mistake,
OL,11,Fit had nothing to do with that kind of
OL,12,Fbehaviour."
OL,14,FMr Gates' ex-wife, Melinda French
OL,15,FGates, recently said the Microsoft co-
OL,16,Ffounder will have to explain his
OL,17,Frelationship with Epstein.
OL,26,@tD@KO]
