OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,F"Whatever questions remain there of
OL,8,Fwhat ` I can't even begin to know all
OL,9,Fof it ` those questions are for those
OL,10,Fpeople and for even my ex-husband.
OL,11,FThey need to answer to those things,
OL,12,Fnot me," she said.
OL,14,FBoth Mr Gates and Ms French Gates, who
OL,15,Fdivorced in 2021, have said that his
OL,16,Frelationship with Epstein created
OL,17,Fproblems in their marriage.
