OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FEarlier this month Mr Gates pulled out
OL,8,Fof delivering a keynote address at an
OL,9,FAI summit in India, the Gates
OL,10,FFoundation confirmed, without
OL,11,Fproviding a reason for the abrupt
OL,12,Fwithdrawal.
OL,14,FMr Gates has come under fire in recent
OL,15,Fweeks over two draft emails in the
OL,16,FDOJ's release, which Epstein appears
OL,17,Fto have written to himself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
