OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772118239
OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,FIn them, Epstein claims he facilitated
OL,8,Fsexual encounters for Mr Gates and
OL,9,Fhelped him obtain medication to hide a
OL,10,Fsexually transmitted infection from
OL,11,Fhis wife.
OL,13,FMr Gates has strongly denied these
OL,14,Fclaims, telling ITV News' North
OL,15,FAmerican partner CNN: "These claims
OL,16,Fare absolutely absurd and completely
OL,17,Ffalse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
