OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772118239
OL,3,CBill Gates admits to affairs with
OL,4,C'Russian women' in meeting about
OL,5,CEpstein links
OL,7,F"The only thing these documents
OL,8,Fdemonstrate is Epstein's frustration
OL,9,Fthat he did not have an ongoing
OL,10,Frelationship with Gates and the
OL,11,Flengths he would go to entrap and
OL,12,Fdefame.
OL,14,F"While Mr Gates acknowledges that
OL,15,Fmeeting with Epstein was a serious
OL,16,Ferror in judgment, he unequivocally
OL,17,Fdenies any improper conduct related to
OL,18,FEpstein and the horrible activities in
OL,19,Fwhich Epstein was involved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
